    "text": "Service-Disabled Veterans Small Business Continuation Act\n\nThis bill enables the surviving spouse of a service-disabled veteran who owned a small business to retain priority of the business for a period of time upon the death of the veteran spouse, regardless of the severity of the veteran's disability."
